[The first milestone would be the identification of the deep learning
architecture that allows us to reduce the loss function in our models.
We will be exploring several architectures using subsets of the
dataset.]{.mark}

[After the identification of the best architecture, the second milestone
would be to analyse all our dataset together and perform data analysis
of the results.]{.mark}

